dct_title_s: Commercial map of the Near East / compiled, engraved and printed by General Drafting Co., Inc [for] Irving National Bank.
dct_description_sm: Relief shown by gradient tints and spot heights. Ancillary maps: Rainfall for January -- Rainfall for July -- Natural vegetation -- Principal products -- Density of population. Map shows Arabian Peninsula undefined boundary, international and provincial boundaries, submarine cables, wireless stations, sea routes distance to ports,
